ARTICLE.TITLE: RBI Grade C Officer Result 2019 Announced @ rbi.org.in
ARTICLE.TEXT:
RBI Grade C Officer Result 2019: Reserve Bank of India (RBI) has released the RBI Grade C Officer Exam 2018 Result on its official website. Now all wait is over for those candidates who have appeared for the RBI Grade C Officer exam. Candidates can check their result on the official website of Reserve Bank of India (RBI)- rbi.org.in.

Reserve Bank of India (RBI) has announced the various posts result under Grade C Posts. Candidates who have applied for the posts like Trade Finance, Corporate Lending, Treasury, Analytics & General Banking, Information Technology and Web Designer posts can check their result available on the official website.

According to the short notification released by the Reserve Bank of India (RBI), not the selected candidates will have to go through the document verification in support of their eligibility. The Board / Bank will cross check the document/s submitted by the candidates in support of their eligibility and other facts.

Reserve Bank of India (RBI) had earlier released the notification for the various posts including Trade Finance, Corporate Lending, Treasury, Analytics & General Banking, Information Technology and Web Designer against Advt. No. 5A/2018-19 dated December 19 2018.



Direct Link for RBI Grade C Officer Result 2019





RBI Grade C Officer Result 2019 Download Process



Visit the official website i.e. https://www.rbi.org.in/

Click the link-Lateral Recruitment of Officers in Grade ‘C’ on Contract Basis – 2018 given on the Home Page.

You will get your desired PDF of the result in a new window open on your screen.

You can take Print Out of your result.
